{"tid":2288284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本首相菅義偉明接待澳洲總理莫里森 料敲定軍事合作協定","createTime":"2020-11-16T11:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-16T12:07:00.000Z","uid":75656,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cdf4819286c8238e8880c1ed7db8b9b48478623","tid":2288284,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:33:45.000Z","msg":"《路透》16日報導，日本首相菅義偉與澳洲總理莫里森，17日預計針對雙方一項歷史性的防禦協定達成意見，加深日本與澳洲的關係，共同對抗不斷擴張影響力的中國。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，莫里森將在17日抵達日本，安全專家預期他會與菅義偉就日澳「相互准入協定」（Reciprocal Access Agreement，RAA）達成最終意見，為兩國軍隊互訪、訓練及共同執行任務建立法律框架。<br />\n<br />\n日本外務省一名官員向媒體表示：「菅義偉與莫里森會晤後，將會有所宣布。」但並未詳加說明。<br />\n<br />\n日澳「相互准入協定」耗時6年協商，日後還須經兩國國會批准，方可生效。該協定將是日本繼1960年與美國簽署「美日安保條約」，允許美國在日本境內派駐戰艦、戰機和軍隊後，再度與外國簽署防禦協定。<br />\n<br />\n由於都對中國在印度－太平洋地區的活動感到憂心，包括推動南海軍事化、在釣魚台列嶼（日稱尖閣諸島）周圍演習，以及持續拉攏太平洋島國等，日澳雙方正尋求加強彼此聯繫。<br />\n<br />\n為了抗衡中國，菅義偉上月才造訪越南和印尼，尋求與2國加強關係。更早前，美國、日本、印度、澳洲等「四方安全對話」（QUAD）國家外交首長，也齊聚東京，被北京視為意圖「小北約」（mini-NATO）組織，目的是遏阻中國擴張。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3353282\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3353282&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=315a01f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3353282&h=7e6b54cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3353282</a><br />\n<br />\n路透社：<a href=\"https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN27W0M6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN27W0M6&d=Mbax9TUBBsNKvtRo7%2B5fu1NDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=4887a6b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FidUSKBN27W0M6&h=8858394f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reuters.com/article/idUSKBN27W0M6</a>"},{"pid":"d18c2d36c3d9d8dfda6c84ec33bdccfd8b328558","tid":2288284,"uid":45830,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"六眼準備中！？"},{"pid":"1f5a54a7ae0c5c1e17a779bd290c0329da965fd4","tid":2288284,"uid":293225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:00:10.000Z","msg":"屌又㩒錯負皮，cancel 唔到。"},{"pid":"f95c8c6d5d5070652797221cb4ec7b5b32207812","tid":2288284,"uid":3149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}